underlying_goal: Fix a production deployment issue where the frontend app was not working, ultimately caused by wrong API_BASE_URL environment variable and missing Supabase env vars
friction_detail: Claude initially added env vars to the wrong Cloud Run region (europe-west2 instead of europe-west1) and misidentified the root cause multiple times before finding the actual issue (wrong API_BASE_URL pointing to the frontend itself).
brief_summary: User needed to fix a broken production frontend deployment; after multiple failed attempts and significant user frustration, Claude eventually identified the wrong API_BASE_URL env var and fixed it successfully.
